OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mixture of bright spells and
OL,6,Fblustery showers, the showers heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes during the morning. Feeling
OL,8,Fchilly in the fresh to strong westerly
OL,9,Fwinds. The showers becoming lighter
OL,10,Fand more scattered through the
OL,11,Fafternoon with winds easing.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FMainly dry at first this
OL,14,Fevening, but thickening cloud bringing
OL,15,Fpatchy light rain to the west coast.
OL,16,FThe patchy light rain extending
OL,17,Feastwards overnight. Winds mostly
OL,18,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
