OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA damp start with patchy
OL,6,Flight rain and drizzle. Soon mainly
OL,7,Fdry and skies brightening, perhaps the
OL,8,Fodd sunny break developing. Feeling
OL,9,Fpleasant in light to moderate
OL,10,Fsouthwest winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA dry
OL,13,Fand bright start on Wednesday, but
OL,14,Frain later. Mainly dry on Thursday and
OL,15,FFriday, best of the brightness on
OL,16,FThursday with the odd shower possible
OL,17,Fon Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
